{"tid":1567010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[又懶人包] 831完全未釋除既疑團: 消防同目擊證人說法 南轅北轍","createTime":"2019-09-14T00:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T10:35:11.000Z","uid":161430,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f1da1a4154abefad83d0f5b2b7519771719a446a","tid":1567010,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T00:53:41.000Z","msg":"宜家簡單總結係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins>消防話：</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n- 冇見到有任何人嘔白泡，個個清醒<br />\n- 冇抬走過任何嘔白泡、昏迷傷者，無論11:10入站既消防或11:30入站既消防PAO<br />\n- 若有傷者在救護人員視線以外被轉移，消防當局無法對此作任何揣測<br />\n(呢個講法就好曖昧)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uPMQq0X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuPMQq0X.png&h=e9e02462&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsource: 明報 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/grpFOeo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgrpFOeo.png&h=71a22869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsource: 立場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>目擊證人話：</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n- 有嘔白泡人士，昏迷不醒 (龍小姐)<br />\n- 警員幫傷者搓心口，但佢毫無反應 (龍小姐)<br />\n- 有女警叫傷者「唔好瞓」(龍小姐)<br />\n- 10分鐘後，有消防抬走佢 (龍小姐)<br />\n- 見到有人昏迷 (David)<br />\n- 昏迷既人係被拖走，冇用擔架床 (David)<br />\n- 有人當場死再被帶走 (早過龍小姐講既網上人士)<br />\n- 有女聲大叫「醒呀」(直播影片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YkOSEmE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYkOSEmE.png&h=5f2d18dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c09RUU3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc09RUU3.png&h=1a0e8ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iBWtcGM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiBWtcGM.png&h=e3da7c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/scnoL3X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FscnoL3X.png&h=1aa2b26a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsource: 立場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟係有一方講大話？<br />\n<br />\n定係兩邊都冇講大話，<br />\n但有不知名人士 (黑警?) /假消防 (黑警?) 帶走昏迷傷者而消防都不知情？"},{"pid":"5ea22e2e1d4c432c76a72e23042f0d2d62a809e5","tid":1567010,"uid":161430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T00:54:37.000Z","msg":"立場LINK<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0fact-check-8-31%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E6%8C%87%E6%8F%AE%E5%AE%98%E7%96%91%E6%93%85%E6%94%B9%E5%82%B7%E8%80%85%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E8%80%85%E7%A8%B1%E9%BB%9E%E7%AE%97%E5%89%8D%E5%B7%B2%E6%9C%89%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7%E7%94%B7%E9%81%AD%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E5%93%A1%E5%B8%B6%E8%B5%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0fact-check-8-31%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%2599%25E6%25B6%2588%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258F%25AE%25E5%25AE%2598%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2593%2585%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2582%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2595%25B8-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E9%25BB%259E%25E7%25AE%2597%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2598%258F%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E7%2594%25B7%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25B6%2588%25E9%2598%25B2%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E8%25B5%25B0%2F&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=be14975f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0fact-check-8-31%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%2599%25E6%25B6%2588%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258F%25AE%25E5%25AE%2598%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2593%2585%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2582%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2595%25B8-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E9%25BB%259E%25E7%25AE%2597%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2598%258F%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E7%2594%25B7%25E9%