>\n因為佢地口供都幾一致，仲有果d係被捕人士，<br />\n仲有親身上埋記者會既人士"},{"pid":"39b5b277cc464e8c45146db52ee0180db785e7d0","tid":1567010,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:09:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f73711d90f1f2d0c40fe63511f64ef3daf81d34","tid":1567010,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:16:28.000Z","msg":"仲有都未去計返 over 24小時封站呢個point呢<br />\n太多疑團"},{"pid":"33a899bc65625f53ec006c1bcc4201aa65718a87","tid":1567010,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:38:05.000Z","msg":"另外立場David見到既昏迷人士<br />\n同龍小姐見既 並非同一人。<br />\n<br />\n龍小姐見到既係非黑衫<br />\nDavid見到既係黑衫。<br />\n<br />\n呢度已經分別係兩個昏迷不醒、被帶走左既傷者。<br />\n而消防話當日就冇同事見到有昏迷既人被帶走<br />\n<br />\n我傾向唔信係目擊證人會集體吹水，<br />\n而且消防同警察都將最初9人 10人傷者最後修正做7人 + 封站過24小時<br />\n都幾肯定隱瞞事實既消防/警方"},{"pid":"b0961a4d43d36b8c61b0a2a82499df64625ee3af","tid":1567010,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:47:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d18b8c0fe911f2b611536bd6c0b0c5c591441fd","tid":1567010,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:50:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"32be976ee892105f5b093d916985d9f1e1b55d88","tid":1567010,"uid":175091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:56:05.000Z","msg":"集中推831太子、915銅記<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1204740b840cb1f8a7ec7bfae4d966af0f323675","tid":1567010,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T02:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0959275e65fb57aae3bed8ad84ae928a0f59676e","tid":1567010,"uid":46457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T02:03:54.000Z","msg":"如果昏迷人士係被拖走而唔係用擔架就非常可疑，可能有人扮消防"},{"pid":"386c8225d3f31e0b4205399f13ea0aacf93d8bc2","tid":1567010,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislik