0Z","msg":"ching講得冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDavid話見到「冇擔架 被拖走」 呢一點 都被人忽漏左 冇咩點提。<br />\n<br />\n其實一個專業既消防救護，無論去救既傷者係消醒與否，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地從來都唔會咁樣冇擔架 拖人走</span></span><br />\n<br />\n拉住人走, 拖住人走既通常係乜野人做？我只有見過黑警會咁做<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/usa/article/882838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fusa%2Farticle%2F882838&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=ac614ee3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/usa/article/882838</a><br />\n大家記唔記得早一個禮拜 又係太子站先有呢單<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/09/20190904_%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99_%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81_%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F09%2F20190904_%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%2599_%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581_%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B_1.jpg&h=512a3b5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>乜野人會強行拖走昏迷、暈倒既人？</strong></span></span><br />\n再講多次，係黑警"},{"pid":"0c77e7225fc540b43303737647c974b970f112d0","tid":1567010,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T08:07:01.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<br />\n過埋今日記者會後<br />\n<br />\n宜家件事幾乎可以確認係:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">目擊證人同消防 兩邊都冇講大話，<br />\n但有不知名人士 (黑警?) /假消防 (黑警?) 帶走昏迷傷者 / 改紀錄，<br />\n而消防都不知情</span>"},{"pid":"808ade3140844317921784fe98756e45ee23e3d7","tid":1567010,"uid":152225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T08:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ce7c7